OL,5,FIt comes after the Supreme Court ruled
OL,6,Fin 2025 that the provision of
OL,7,FChristian religious education at
OL,8,Fschools in Northern Ireland does not
OL,9,Fcomply with human rights standards.
OL,11,FThe court upheld an appeal brought by
OL,12,Fa pupil at a Belfast school and her
OL,13,Ffather and reinstated an earlier court
OL,14,Fruling that the teaching of RE and
OL,15,Fcollective worship breaches human
OL,16,Frights as it does not approach the
OL,17,Fsubject in an "objective, critical and
OL,18,Fpluralist manner".
