OL,5,FMr Givan responded to that judgment in
OL,6,Fthe Assembly chamber on Tuesday
OL,7,Fmorning announcing a revision of the
OL,8,Freligious education curriculum as well
OL,9,Fas formal inspections across all
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FThe review is to be led by a Professor
OL,13,Ffrom Stranmillis University College
OL,14,Fand a former primary school principal,
OL,15,Fsupported by a group of teachers.
OL,17,FIt is also to involve extensive
OL,18,Fengagement with churches, teachers,
OL,19,Fschool leaders, parents and young
OL,20,Fpeople.
