OL,5,FThe Minister asserted that the review
OL,6,Fwill develop a revised RE syllabus
OL,7,Fconsistent with the Supreme Court
OL,8,Fjudgment.
OL,10,F"The time is now right for a review of
OL,11,Fa syllabus, it has been nearly 20
OL,12,Fyears since it was last revised, a
OL,13,Fwider curriculum review is already
OL,14,Funder way," he said.
OL,16,F"I am especially mindful of the need
OL,17,Fto safeguard religious education as an
OL,18,Fimportant academic discipline within
OL,19,Fthe curriculum.
