OL,5,F"A useful and enriching knowledge of
OL,6,FChristianity and more widely the
OL,7,Fworld's main religious and
OL,8,Fphilosophical traditions, studied with
OL,9,Facademic rigour, will be the ambition
OL,10,Fof the new syllabus"
OL,12,FHe added: "However, let me be clear,
OL,13,Fand as upheld by the court,
OL,14,FChristianity will remain central to
OL,15,Fthe revised syllabus.
OL,17,F"The reality of Northern Ireland's
OL,18,Fhistorical, cultural and legal context
OL,19,Fmeans that Christianity should and
OL,20,Fwill continue to be the primary focus
OL,21,Fon the revised syllabus."
