OL,5,FThe announcement has been welcomed by
OL,6,Fthe Protestants Representative Body
OL,7,Ffor Education.
OL,9,FVice Chair Dr Anita Gracie works at
OL,10,FStranmillis University College
OL,11,Fteaching student teachers religious
OL,12,Feducation.J"I think the teacher's
OL,13,Fexperience has changed over the years.
