OL,5,F"In the past, it was very much about
OL,6,Fpassing on the faith, whereas now it's
OL,7,Fvery much encouraging children to
OL,8,Fthink about issues of faith and life's
OL,9,Fbig questions, and how they answer
OL,10,Fthat will very much come from their
OL,11,Fown backgrounds and identities and
OL,12,Fviewpoints.
OL,14,F"So our role as teachers is to help
OL,15,Fthem to come to their own decisions
OL,16,Frather than just passing down ready-
OL,17,Fmade answers that we have from
OL,18,Fteaching, as we have done in the past
OL,19,Ffrom our own heritage," she said.
