OL,5,FHumanist campaigners remain uncertain
OL,6,Fthat the announcement goes far enough.
OL,8,FBoyd Sleator said: "The RE curriculum
OL,9,Fneeds to be broad and balanced and we
OL,10,Fneed to make sure that there are
OL,11,FHumanist voices included in that
OL,12,Freview.
OL,14,F"With regards to opt out, we need to
OL,15,Fmake sure that children are not
OL,16,Fstigmatised.JFollowing a public
OL,17,Fconsultation, it's hoped the new
OL,18,Fsyllabus will be in place by September
OL,19,F2027.
